---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Our Services - PT. Recruvy International Group"
  description="Comprehensive recruitment services and solutions across multiple industries. Learn about our recruitment process and industries we serve."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary text-white py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Our Services</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Comprehensive recruitment solutions tailored to your business needs
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Our Recruitment Process</h2>
        <p class="section-subheading">
          A systematic approach to finding the perfect talent for your organization
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold">
            1
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-darkgray mb-3">Client Consultation & Job Analysis</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              We begin by understanding your organization's culture, values, and specific requirements. Our team conducts a thorough analysis of the job role, required skills, and ideal candidate profile to ensure we find the perfect match for your organization.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold">
            2
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-darkgray mb-3">Candidate Sourcing & Screening</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Leveraging our extensive talent network and advanced sourcing strategies, we identify and attract top-quality candidates. Our rigorous screening process includes background verification, skills assessment, and cultural fit evaluation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold">
            3
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-darkgray mb-3">Interview Coordination</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              We facilitate seamless interview coordination between candidates and your hiring team. Our team handles scheduling, provides interview preparation support, and gathers comprehensive feedback to ensure an efficient hiring process.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold">
            4
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-darkgray mb-3">Offer Management</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              We assist in salary negotiations and offer management to ensure a smooth acceptance process. Our team acts as a liaison between you and the candidate, helping to address concerns and finalize employment terms.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold">
            5
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-darkgray mb-3">Onboarding Support</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Our support continues beyond placement. We provide comprehensive onboarding assistance to ensure new hires integrate smoothly into your organization, setting the foundation for long-term success and retention.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-lightbg">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Industries We Serve</h2>
        <p class="section-subheading">
          Specialized recruitment solutions across diverse sectors
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-darkgray mb-3">Information Technology</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Connecting tech companies with skilled software developers, data scientists, cybersecurity experts, and IT professionals across all specializations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-secondary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-darkgray mb-3">Finance & Banking</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Recruiting top financial analysts, investment bankers, accountants, and banking professionals for financial institutions and corporate finance teams.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-darkgray mb-3">Healthcare & Pharmaceuticals</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Sourcing qualified healthcare professionals, medical specialists, pharmaceutical researchers, and healthcare administrators for medical institutions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"></path>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-darkgray mb-3">Manufacturing & Engineering</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Finding skilled engineers, production managers, quality control specialists, and technical professionals for manufacturing and industrial operations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-secondary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-darkgray mb-3">Retail & E-commerce</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Recruiting retail managers, e-commerce specialists, supply chain professionals, and customer service experts for retail and online businesses.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-darkgray mb-3">Professional Services</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Placing consultants, legal professionals, marketing experts, HR specialists, and other professional service providers across various industries.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-primary text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        Ready to Start Your Recruitment Journey?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-gray-100">
        Let us help you find the perfect candidates for your organization
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">
        Contact Us Today
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
